  "body": "Notes for debugging:\r\n\r\n1. The branch is `epoch-processing-test-runner-part1`\r\n2. Here is the [test](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/cd83653ae1fa79466a98ad94f72f17bfcabcf1b3/beacon-chain/core/epoch/spectest/epoch_processing_crosslink_test.go)\r\n3. Running the test, you'll see test cases `single_crosslink_update_from_current_epoch` and `single_crosslink_update_from_previous_epoch` fail\r\n4. We can first begin to look at why [single_crosslink_update_from_current_epoch](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/cd83653ae1fa79466a98ad94f72f17bfcabcf1b3/beacon-chain/core/epoch/spectest/crosslinks_minimal.yaml#L1893) fail\r\n5. The [condition](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/0321d1b42a44fdfbcbac0994d945ec8458dbafee/beacon-chain/core/epoch/epoch_processing.go) we want to satisfy here is `tree_hash_root(state.current_crosslink[7]) == attestation.data.crosslink.parent_root`\r\nThis is `attestation.data.crosslink.parent_root`:\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/cd83653ae1fa79466a98ad94f72f17bfcabcf1b3/beacon-chain/core/epoch/spectest/crosslinks_minimal.yaml#L2209\r\nThis is `state.current_crosslink[7]`\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/cd83653ae1fa79466a98ad94f72f17bfcabcf1b3/beacon-chain/core/epoch/spectest/crosslinks_minimal.yaml#L2235\r\n\r\n6. We need to look into why `tree_hash_root(state.current_crosslink[7])` yields a different result than `x4AJ/fB/xWoR8SI3BlijU6qlQu1j5ExLwV/0zRBaszw=` which is ",
